0:16:30.100,0:16:31.380
Kwete

0:16:31.380,0:16:35.220
Pasi rino, hapana mushumiri wa Mwari.

0:16:35.220,0:16:37.980
Asi ini ndichiri pakati penyu.

0:16:37.980,0:16:44.080
Pakanga pane zvakakwana zvaifanira kundidzingira kunze kwe Nigeria, Africa.

0:16:44.080,0:16:52.160
Asi ini ndaienda ku musangano, uye ku misangano, maigara muchiona nhandare izere.

0:16:52.160,0:16:55.780
Nyika, vashumiri - vose vanoungana.

0:16:55.780,0:17:01.040
Asi ini handiyedzwe neizvozvo; Mushure memusangano - ndodzoka kumusha.

0:17:01.040,0:17:04.760
Ndodzoka ku Africa uko ndiri kutambudzwa,

0:17:04.760,0:17:13.460
Kwavanoda kundiuraya, kundiparadzwe.

0:17:13.460,0:17:20.180
Ndinogara kwandisinga pembedzwe; Ndakabva kunzvimbo yandinopembererwa.

0:17:20.180,0:17:24.360
Ndino pembererwa pasi rose asi ndakasiya nzvimbo iyoyo.

0:17:24.360,0:17:29.580
Ndinogara kwandisinga pembererwe.

0:17:29.580,0:17:33.780
Ndinoda kunyengetera nemi. Isai chinhu ichi shure kwenyu kuitira kuti tigone kufambira mberi.

0:17:33.780,0:17:39.900
Ndiri kungotaura zvinoitika, rwendo rwacho kusvika pari zvino.

0:17:39.900,0:17:41.920
Zvakanaka.

0:17:41.920,0:17:57.500
Kotamisa musoro wako ukumbira Mwari kuti akupe mwoyo unonzwa, muzita ra Jesu Kristu.

0:17:57.500,0:18:02.480
Kumbira Mwari kuti akupe simba, kuti usaite chiramwa.

0:18:02.480,0:18:04.020
Usaramwe

0:18:04.020,0:18:10.600
Pausinga pembererwe ndiyo nzvimbo yakanakisisa yekugara, kuti uwane simba.

0:18:10.600,0:18:17.000
Kana uri pakati pehondo, unozvivaka; izvozvo zvakanaka.

0:18:17.000,0:18:22.360
Kwausinga pembererwe, kwauri kutambudzwa ndiyo nzvimbo yakanakisisa yokuti iwe urarame.

0:18:22.360,0:18:26.180
Zvichakuumba iwe; Zvose izvi zvichakuumba.

0:18:26.180,0:18:29.480
Goridhe haigone kuva goridhe isina kupfuura ne mubisiro.

0:18:29.480,0:18:32.900
Unhu hwevanhu hunofanirwawo kupfuura nemubisiro.

0:18:32.900,0:18:41.380
Ndicho chikonzero ndakasarudza kugara kwandisinga pemberererwe - muno mu Nigeria, muno mu Africa.

0:18:41.380,0:18:46.360
Ndakagara muno kuti ndivake nyasha dza Mwari.

0:18:46.360,0:18:50.440
Kana nyasha dza Mwari dziri pakati pezvinetso, dzino nyanya kusimba.

0:18:50.440,0:18:53.420
Saka ndicho chikonzero ndakagara pakati penyu.

0:18:53.420,0:18:59.520
Kumbira Mwari kuti akupe nyasha dzekugara uko usinga pembererwe.

